        "comment": "- I was a little bit busy by Hermione's bug - I never see that before and Hermione's head is my visual inde -, and until Flitwick, I get this lost-time bug in my mind. \r\nAnd I completely troll Flitwick and Key's Room in the End - and Fred & George Market. \r\n- But I get a pretty good RNG for SW and some encounters, but the last in Forbidden Forest made me angry. Without my troll at Flitwick & F/G's Market, it was under 1.17 run by far or maybe even under 1.16 run.\r\n\r\nBefore the story of this re-timed run, i make a summary of this for everyone who doesn't want to got the full story :p\r\n\r\nSo:\r\n- I record a new PB which was 1.17.02.6x but my LiveSplit's record failed (it was deleted i don't know why).\r\n- I re-timed it but I fucked up LiveSplit Settings (which was already fucked up in video, I commented it since the begining, that explain the sound \"It's Levioosa, not Leviosaa\", I can't delete this sound without delete the in-game sound)\r\n- I decided to change my LiveSplit Profile with another and re-timed it another with rights settings and video record.\r\n- And I retimed the final Split that explain why the PB is 1.17.03 and not 1.17.02.\r\n- It was 1.17.03.18 which is the right frames who count, in video we can see the timer was 1.17.03.57. But when the run starts, I press my Start button on LiveSplit a little bit late, so I calculated that time lost was 0.25ms so it's 1.17.03.18 + 0.0.0.25 = 1.17.03.43.\r\n\r\n\r\nDetailed Story available when you click on the title of this video and to look the description below the YouTube video: (which is not rly more detailed thank you think)\r\n\r\n",
